Title: Light Power Check
ShieldStart:
G90
G28T
M106P0S255
[[GPIOHigh 40]]
[[ExecReturn sudo /home/pi/versus_config/projectorOn.sh > /dev/null]]
[[ExecReturn echo "$(date) - [Light power calibration] Starting light power check job" >> /home/pi/logs/versus.log]]
[[ExecReturn echo "$(date)" >> /home/pi/logs/logProjector.log]]
[[ExecReturn sudo /usr/local/bin/setProjectorLight 250 500 [[LampHours]] >> /home/pi/logs/logProjector.log]]
[[ExecReturn echo "$(date) - [Light power calibration] Setting Light output to:" [[LampHours]] >> /home/pi/logs/versus.log]]
[[ExecReturn echo "$(date) - [Light power calibration] Setting Light output to:" [[LampHours]] >> /home/pi/logs/logProjector.log]]
